title: 136: Which teams are in the QB market?
itunes:title: 136: Which teams are in the QB market?
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks discuss which NFL teams will be in the market for a new quarterback this offseason. The duo also looks ahead to Week 11 in the NFL and make their college football picks.
